workspace_structure.description:
The workspace is partitioned as follows. The PD manages project-director/ exclusively;
the feature-developer manages feature/; the Vision Hasher writes to vision/;
the knowledge/ area is shared.

step.action:
Store the configuration in state.json (mcp_available/mcp_name/verified initially false/null/false — populated by verification below):
                  smoke_test_automation: {
                    enabled: true,
                    environments: {
                      web: { base_url: "[user-provided]", auth: null, mcp_available: false, mcp_name: null, verified: false },
                      native: { app_id: "[user-provided or null]", appium_endpoint: "[user-provided or http://localhost:4723]", mcp_available: false, mcp_name: null, verified: false },
                      desktop: { executable_path: "[user-provided or null]", window_title: "[user-provided or null]", mcp_available: false, mcp_name: null, verified: false }
                    },
                    missing_prerequisites: []
                  }

Store in state.json:
                  smoke_test_automation: {
                    enabled: false,
                    environments: { web: null, native: null, desktop: null },
                    missing_prerequisites: []
                  }
